RSE Asia


Welcome! This is the website of the Research Software Engineering (RSE) Asia Association. The RSE Asia Association is built as a project under the Open Life Science program (OLS-4).




The RSE Asia Association was launched on Thursday, 14th October 2021. This day holds special significance as being the first International RSE Day! At the launch event we conducted activities for contributing to Hacktoberfest 2021.




This is our official logo!

This website is built using the distill package. The source code for this website is located in the RSE_Asia GitHub repository.
We abide by the Society of Research Software Engineering code of conduct.
Follow our updates on Twitter at the handle RSE_Asia.

articles.title: Membership
articles.description: To become a community member of the RSE Asia Association, please fill this short [membership form](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSci4FOE7wBeDJQowDSmweujLhJFfzr2rut46yKJc0agkE7Jug/viewform). The community membership of the RSE Asia Association is free and open to all. People from all regions of the globe are welcome to join our community, irrespective of whether they belong to or are located in Asia.
